    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/91895f9861eb637d09c3604515bebddf.avif?t=1635753620\" width=626 height=259 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >置身于遥远的未来，领略后启示录世界的黑暗历史</h2>《After Shadows》是一款类银河恶魔城+平台跳跃的游戏。故事的舞台设定在遥远的未来，世界末日之后，人类早已灭绝，人类文明也荡然无存，只留下些许模糊而又遥远的记忆。而奇异的生物在大地上复苏，成了世界的新主人。<br><br><br>黑暗怪物袭击了村子，感染了安娜的母亲。你将化身半精灵安娜，探索古老的废弃堡垒，为母亲寻找解药。这座废弃的堡垒危机四伏，谁也不知道里面究竟有什么东西。它无比巨大，堡垒的底部甚至突破了地底的界限，一路延伸到了可怕的原始黑暗之中。传说有云，潜入这片黑暗中的勇敢冒险家，最终会找到救赎和死亡。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/3b760e475c5ac517e351963288f206ee.poster.avif?t=1635753620\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/3b760e475c5ac517e351963288f206ee.webm?t=1635753620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/3b760e475c5ac517e351963288f206ee.mp4?t=1635753620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>高难度</strong><br>在遥远的未来，弱者没有容身之地。探索废弃堡垒的时候要打起十二万分的精神，一个不小心就有可能落入死亡的阴影之中。你想直接从这只可爱的小鸟身上跑过去？啪，你死啦。你跑得太快，不小心踩到了几根树枝？啪，你又死啦。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/7dc0d8403116c3aeaa610ec788684601.poster.avif?t=1635753620\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/7dc0d8403116c3aeaa610ec788684601.webm?t=1635753620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/7dc0d8403116c3aeaa610ec788684601.mp4?t=1635753620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>自定义角色装备，玩法更多样</strong><br>不管是死亡还是胜利，都会影响到你接下来的冒险之旅。如果你顺利激活了所有水晶，就会随机获得一个奖励装备，如果你不幸死亡，重来时就会随机获得一个诅咒。这些设定无疑会让游戏玩法更加多样。 </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>高度可重玩性</strong><br>盘踞在堡垒中的黑暗会想方设法阻止你到达出口。每次重开游戏，地图都会不一样，有时只有几条路变了，有时是整个地图都变了样。毕竟在永恒之夜里，黑暗才是永远的主宰，恐怖骇人之物更是无处不在。擦亮眼睛，保持清醒吧，冒险家！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/6f7377842e76342fe872110534dbe71f.poster.avif?t=1635753620\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/6f7377842e76342fe872110534dbe71f.webm?t=1635753620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/6f7377842e76342fe872110534dbe71f.mp4?t=1635753620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>黑暗而又充满魅力的世界</strong><br>堡垒中有许多奇奇怪怪的生物，记得跟他们互动。不管是水之恶魔还是全金属机器人，他们都有可能是你冒险之路上的贵人。不过也别忘了，并非所有生物都是友善的……</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>动听的原声音轨</strong><br>黑暗而又动听的原声音轨让你一秒沦陷，彻底沉浸在《After Shadows》的世界里。令人战栗，引人深思，令人沉醉……各种曲风不同的配乐尽在《After Shadows》！  </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>漂亮的游戏画面</strong><br>游戏中的每一块石头、每一只生物，甚至是每一个纹理都是纯手绘的。《After Shadows》注重每一个边角细节，力求呈现出一个栩栩如生的后启示录世界.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/12606ff63a8ec4b3f8c7db10c218a647.poster.avif?t=1635753620\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/12606ff63a8ec4b3f8c7db10c218a647.webm?t=1635753620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/12606ff63a8ec4b3f8c7db10c218a647.mp4?t=1635753620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>多结局</strong><br>选择自己的道路，迎接属于你自己的结局。没错，我们不会去“教”玩家玩游戏，更不会“要求”玩家跟着我们的想法来玩游戏。毕竟游戏的玩法机制应该服务玩家，而不是让玩家去跟着设计好的路来走。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/2847bad76cc46684cb84684c0dfb2eca.poster.avif?t=1635753620\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/2847bad76cc46684cb84684c0dfb2eca.webm?t=1635753620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621420/extras/2847bad76cc46684cb84684c0dfb2eca.mp4?t=1635753620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>游戏幕后</strong><br>我们只是一个开发独立游戏的小团队，人手和资金都比不了大厂。但是我们还是尽力用好手头的资源，一直努力打磨游戏，让它变得更加好玩有趣。希望你会喜欢我们的游戏！</li></ul>",
